  <description>Exports file as indexed image.</description>
  <command interpreter="bash">
    export_to_vcell.sh $input
  </command>
  <inputs>
    <param format="tiff" name="input" type="data" label="2D images"></param>
  </inputs>
  <outputs>
    <data format="tiff" name="output" from_work_dir="output.tif"/>
  </outputs>
<help>

**Description**

Exports a 2D synthetic image as a indexed image that can be imported to VCell as a geometric model.

-----

**Input**

- 2D synthetic image

-----

**Output**

- An indexed image.
</help>
</tool>
